        Real Estate Agent Commission in Queensland: What Sellers Pay and Why
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Commission is one of the biggest costs of selling your home. Here's how it works in Queensland, what's negotiable, and how to think about value rather than just rate.
      </p>
